Last updated: October 16, 2025

ArtQuest (“the App”) is developed and published by MagdaDoesApps (“we,” “our,” or “us”).
We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.
This Privacy Policy explains how ArtQuest handles data and user information.

1. Information We Collect
ArtQuest does not collect, store, or share any personal data on our servers.
All information related to your drawings, levels, and badges is stored locally on your device only.

You do not need to create an account or provide any personal information to use ArtQuest.

2. Access to Device Storage
ArtQuest may request access to your photo library or device storage.
This permission is used only so that you can:
- Save your drawings or progress locally, and
- View or manage your own images within the app.
- We do not upload, share, or transmit any of your files or media to our servers or any third parties.

3. WebView and External Links
ArtQuest includes an in-app WebView feature that allows you to visit external websites where you can purchase physical goods or view related content.
Please note:
These websites are operated by third parties.
MagdaDoesApps is not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites.
We recommend reviewing the privacy policies of any third-party websites you visit through the app.

4. Children’s Privacy
ArtQuest is intended for general audiences but is not designed for children under 13 years old.
We do not knowingly collect or store any information from children.

5. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically.
When we do, we will update the “Last updated” date above.
By continuing to use ArtQuest after any updates, you agree to the revised policy.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
magdadoesapps@gmail.com
